OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775873035
OL,3,CFirst manned Moon mission in more than
OL,4,C50 years splashes down after epic
OL,5,Cvoyage
OL,7,FAlongside their other duties, it
OL,8,Fprovided the opportunity for the team
OL,9,Fto take some spectacular pictures of
OL,10,Fthe Moon and Earth, including a total
OL,11,Fsolar eclipse.
OL,13,FThe Goonhilly Earth Station, near
OL,14,FHelston, in Cornwall, helped track the
OL,15,Fflight.
OL,17,FThe last time Nasa sent astronauts to
OL,18,Fthe Moon was as part of the Apollo 17
OL,19,Fmission in 1972.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
