PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775873035
OL,3,CFirst manned Moon mission in more than
OL,4,C50 years splashes down after epic
OL,5,Cvoyage
OL,7,FThe agency is seeking to return a crew
OL,8,Fto the lunar surface by 2028, before
OL,9,FChina does in about 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
